name: CANYON GOD
description:
You have Summoned the Canyon God.

Unforgiving and scarce with life this environment is not for the faint of heart. With so little given; you have now gained the ability to live with the most of what little has been given to you. Relish in knowing while others grow weak from a pampered life, you have the ability to survive off of little and rise where they will inevitably fall in such conditions. 

You are now a God in this domain.
